00:23:19.680 --> 00:23:24.580
at least one of us made it
out of this worthless place.

00:23:25.660 --> 00:23:28.900
As someone whose relative told her,

00:23:28.900 --> 00:23:33.402
isn't Carnegie Mellon a bit
too advanced for you?

00:23:33.402 --> 00:23:37.679
I am immensely proud to
be a part of this campus.

00:23:37.679 --> 00:23:40.783
And I am so
proud to be able to walk with you today.

00:23:40.783 --> 00:23:50.783
&gt;&gt; [APPLAUSE]

00:23:54.693 --> 00:23:56.559
&gt;&gt; But what now?

