00:59:46.865 --> 00:59:55.140
We're not only inspired by your words but
also motivated by your example.

00:59:55.140 --> 00:59:58.590
It's been an honor to have
you as our keynote speaker.

00:59:58.590 --> 00:59:59.570
Thank you, again, Meg.

